Better Expenses - Personal and Group Expense Tracker App - Legal Information: Better Expenses is here to help to track and manage personal and group expenses. However Better Expenses will not ask you to pay using any ways except using payments through Apple App Store. Also, Better Expenses does not require to submit any users personal data. All data inputted by user is stored only locally on users device and in iCloud in that way so Better Expenses cannot access users data. Better Expenses cannot be held responsible for any successfull or unsuccessfull notifiying about users inputted data, such as notifications about future subscriptions or payments.
